{"tid":524003,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"孔劉閃婚《屍殺列車》孕婦？！婚宴地點也爆出","createTime":"2018-01-09T06:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T08:04:48.000Z","uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39493b54e11e4aa9f2cdb18f1b9058d35fabd5de","tid":524003,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/144929_bf60db7a8d0264beb30765e7c7531257.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F144929_bf60db7a8d0264beb30765e7c7531257.jpg&h=02ee8207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n38歲韓國男星孔劉驚傳婚訊，與合作賣座電影《屍殺列車》的「地表最強孕婦」鄭有美爆出將結婚，同屬Management Soop經紀公司的兩人未傳過緋聞，但孔劉之前受訪時曾說很喜歡鄭有美這個演員，希望有機會能和對方合演愛情戲。同樣出身釜山的兩人私交不錯，還曾聊到有機會想一起用釜山方言拍戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/145010_f0cb779d5509d9ca05b3e73a0c51078b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F145010_f0cb779d5509d9ca05b3e73a0c51078b.jpg&h=da1a777b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n孔劉與34歲鄭有美曾在電影《熔爐》聯手解救受虐學生，之後都因《屍速列車》事業創高峰，網路上突然爆出兩人婚訊，甚至提及已在首爾預定新羅酒店，也就是「雙宋」大婚同地點辦婚宴，但此事已被經紀公司全盤否認，表示傳聞太荒謬，他們兩人的感情就像手足，結婚傳言完全是子虛烏有。"},{"pid":"1889725eab966605905c53004a3e00b916fab7b7","tid":524003,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:40:31.000Z","msg":"生過都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a3c9afe2803fe5d153840151827c2e3fdef010","tid":524003,"uid":10874,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1889725eab966605905c53004a3e00b916fab7b7","tid":524003,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:40:31.000Z","msg":"生過都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1554c012390265871f06e1ca45